  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of a loan of up to &#x20AC;25m to support the development of the wholesale  and retail operations of  The SPAR Group Limited in the Polish market. The  Bank&apos;s loan will include a &#x20AC;5m capex tranche, an &#x20AC;8m tranche for general  corporate purposes and a &#x20AC;12m tranche (uncommitted, commitment of this tranche  will be delegated to Management) to be utilised for completing the  restructuring of &quot;Piotr i Pawel&quot;, one of the Group&apos;s subsidiaries. The loan  will be made available to the Borrower in EUR or PLN.</narrative>
